{"tid":875948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★阿里巴巴否認無人超市虧損百億","createTime":"2018-10-25T08:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T09:43:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5e33a3dccb78822e6346d8d12c02d44882198ee9","tid":875948,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"10月25日下午消息，針對網絡中有關阿里無人超市帶來100億虧損的言論，阿里巴巴發布文章闢謠稱，阿里確實做過一個未來商店的概念設想館，但從沒有投入推廣，更沒有&ldquo;瘋狂投資百億&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n2017年7月，在第二屆淘寶造物節現場，阿里巴巴&ldquo;無人便利店&rdquo;正式對公眾亮相，官方稱其為&ldquo;淘寶會員店&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴新零售技術事業群資深技術專家鄭恩陽接受媒體採訪時表示，&ldquo;這就是一個快閃店，我們這次嘗試的技術會不斷迭代，但不是為了無人店去刻意研發的，對我們來說，最重要的還是提升購物的效率和線下購物體驗。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n以下為聲明全文：<br />\n<br />\n每天都有很多&ldquo;小編&rdquo;在幫阿里各種投資和戰略規劃&hellip;&hellip;你們辛苦了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我們確實做過一個未來商店的概念設想館，但僅限於此，目的是為了告訴大家未來商店的可能，及未來的無限可能。我們從沒有投入推廣，更沒有像這幾位小編所說的&ldquo;瘋狂投資百億&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/crawl/579/w550h829/20181025/CAjA-hmxrkzw6688735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2Fcrawl%2F579%2Fw550h829%2F20181025%2FCAjA-hmxrkzw6688735.jpg&h=a0616bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/crawl/668/w550h918/20181025/cmt9-hmxrkzw6688909.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2Fcrawl%2F668%2Fw550h918%2F20181025%2Fcmt9-hmxrkzw6688909.jpg&h=f08b2dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/crawl/304/w550h554/20181025/_Vns-hmxrkzw6689405.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2Fcrawl%2F304%2Fw550h554%2F20181025%2F_Vns-hmxrkzw6689405.jpg&h=be2ad54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們曾就此多次說明，但依然擋不住小編們的熱情&hellip;&hellip;用了十秒鐘，敲了敲鍵盤，他們就替我們&ldquo;官宣&rdquo;了阿里為無人超市&ldquo;剁手&rdquo;了100多個億、阿里為某挖礦平台投資了幾百億、阿里要裁員50%並全面縮減招聘、甚至說馬雲緊急召集高管開會一整天對未來極度悲觀&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/crawl/284/w448h636/20181025/Wc1M-hmxrkzw6689548.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2Fcrawl%2F284%2Fw448h636%2F20181025%2FWc1M-hmxrkzw6689548.jpg&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1MkgtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=e69fac3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/crawl/284/w448h636/20181025/Wc1M-hmxrkzw6689548.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/390/790.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F390%2F790.htm&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1MkgtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=ae7d8b46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/390/790.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d0ff196b90497794cf93d3b819294e517020bc35","tid":875948,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a18cb3ebec01bf3f7bc24578321fe658c8c49d8","tid":875948,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}